title: Ebro In The Morning - Mase Disses Diddy + Rest In Peace Scott Hall
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 3/15/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing NYC FC, Mase Dissing Diddy, and the passing of wrestling legend Scott Hall. 

Get excited for the gurus to help solve your problems and get the latest news with Flashing Lights. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
